short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bring holiday cheer to your Chrome with a festive Christmas tree in town live wallpaper.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bring the holiday spirit to your browser with the Christmas Tree in Town Live Wallpaper. This Chrome extension features a beautifully decorated Christmas tree standing tall in the heart of a festive town. Surrounded by twinkling lights, snow, and the warmth of the season, this live wallpaper will fill every new tab with holiday cheer and joy.

Features:
🎄 Gorgeous live wallpaper showcasing a Christmas tree in a festive town.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display to help keep you on track during the holiday season.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts to navigate your favorite sites effortlessly.
Embrace the holiday season and let the beauty of a Christmas tree in town transform your browsing experience with every new tab.
